{
  "stem": "22047.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're fighting them because they attacked us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we're over there because there's a job to be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's a-- there's a monster trying to take over the world in Europe, and he just about almost did it in Hitler and his folks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I-- I felt no resentment at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I felt that's-- that's my duty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's my job.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've gotta go through with it, as much as I-- there was a lot of-- a lot of trauma associated with-- with going into combat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, well, as you know, I'm-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was right after I came home after OCS.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said that we're-- we're going in to-- I'm going to be assigned to this division in Oklahoma, 42nd Division, and before I go-- of course, I never got to see her beyond that time, because we were so involved in Oklahoma, and so I didn't come home again.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did call her and talk to her on the phone and tell her that we were going overseas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't say a whole lot, because the-- the censors would have gotten upset with me if I had said a whole lot about where we were going or what-- where-- what sector of Europe we were going to.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't tell her that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did tell her I loved her, and-- and I'll be back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I corresponded with her all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, again, he was very militarily oriented, and he felt very proud that I was going into combat, particularly since I was an officer and had a responsibility.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was, I think, pretty proud.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
